tool_description.description:
Generates exercises for english lessons on the given topic. This is grammar exercise, that helps us to learn past simple and past continoues, so please give in the brackets next to the blank spot verb. In the given structure. In the tag returns a list of objects wih 2 fields CONTENT and ANSWER. Create exercise that way where all answers are different. Please take into account level of language that is given as a parameter.
{{CONTENT}} {{ANSWER}}
- content: string, Only one sentence of exercise - correct_answer: string, a correct answer for the exercise
